                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6213" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1574</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8454 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深耕其修远，扬帆但信风——东方雨虹的多元化之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Stay Gold and Set Sail  - The Diversification of Oriental Yuhong</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙琦，徐维东，罗紫珺，高亚亚</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京东方雨虹防水技术股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">多元化；发展战略；竞争优势；建筑建材</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Diversification; Development Strategy; Competitive Advantage; Building Materials</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例呈现了李卫国带领东方雨虹成为防水第一品牌，之后又成为建筑建材系统服务商的历程。首先，案例介绍了东方雨虹抓住毛主席纪念堂防水维修工程等机遇，锻造产品和服务质量，并完成全国产能扩张，抢占布局广度；其次，尽管公司在防水领域已成翘楚，却面临着激烈竞争。同时受市场时刻变化的影响，公司股价经历过三次重大下跌。于是公司开始向行业上下游和相关产业链探索扩张，形成了以主营防水业务为核心，建筑涂料、节能保温、特种砂浆、非织造布等多品类齐头并进的建筑建材系统服务体系。然而，在扩张过程中，公司仍需面对资金承压、质量问题等扩张难题。本案例将启发学生了解多元化战略的内涵、类型，掌握多元化战略的实现途径，理解多元化战略的优势及风险，并可以引导学生思考东方雨虹未来如何加强多元业务的协同发展，以创造持续竞争优势。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes how Li Weiguo led Oriental Yuhong to develop into the best waterproof brand and then transform to a building materials system service provider. Firstly, the case introduces that Oriental Yuhong seized development opportunities and completed the expansion of national production capacity to get the regional breadth while guaranteeing the quality of its products and service. Secondly, although Oriental had made a great success in the waterproof field, there was fierce competition in the field. Since negative market changes may arise any time, the company&#39;s share price has experienced three major declines. As a result, this company began to explore the upstream and downstream of the industry and related industrial chain. It has formed a building materials service system with the main waterproof business as the core, building coatings, energy saving, thermal insulation, special mortar, nonwovens and other categories developing in the same time. However, in the process of expansion, the company still needs to face capital pressure and quality problems. This case can inspire students to learn the connotation and types of diversification strategy, grasp how diversification strategy can be implemented while understanding advantages and risks of the strategy. What’s more, students can think about what Oriental Yuhong can do to strengthen its coordinated development of multiple businesses, so that the competitive advantage can be sustained.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业多元化</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
